<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;" align="justify">You can also eat garlic that can give instant and temporary relief from the discomforts brought about by <a href="http://www.yeastinfectionreliefblog.com/yeastinfectionomore" target="_blank">yeast infection</a>. Application of apple cider vinegar into your bath water is also beneficial. It helps alleviate the itching of the external skin. Drink lots of water.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;" align="justify">You can try applying oregano oil, because like garlic, it gives comfort. Limit your intake of antibiotics; stop all together if you are already well. Do not douche because it&#8217;ll only disturb the pH of the vagina which could lead to multiplication of bacteria and yeast. Do not wear tight fitting clothes and wear clothes made of cotton.</p>
