<p style="margin-bottom: 0.42cm; text-indent: 1.27cm;">Try some anti-<strong>candida recipes</strong> that will not only add variety to your regular meals but also offer tremendous health-boosting nutrients.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.42cm; text-indent: 1.27cm;">Limit intake of sugar and refined carbohydrates. Steamed vegetables, with nutrients still intact, are among the recommended items. Note that improving your glucose tolerance can help manage chronic candidiasis.</p>
