When it is found on parts such as the mouth, these are called mouth thrush or moniliasis. [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/yeast-infection-relief-blog/Yeast_Infection_Relief_Blog-What_You_Need_to_Know_About_Candida_Fungus.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm;" align="justify">Candidiasis is a vaginal infection that came from formation of <strong>candida fungus</strong>, specifically that of candida albicans strains.  It is normally seen in the areas of the vagina and some parts of the mouth or wherever it is damp.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm;" align="justify">When it is found on parts such as the mouth, these are called mouth thrush or moniliasis. When in antibiotic therapy, it weakens the body&#8217;s resistance and immune system at the same time. This results to multiplication of the fungus.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm;" align="justify">These are commonly seen in people suffering from diabetes, people experiencing hormonal changes like in pregnancy, intake of birth control pills and those who have weakened immune system.</p>
