<p>Some of the main causes of this condition have been found to be birth control medication, steroids and antibiotic use. One of the main natural treatments for yeast infection has been to look at one&#8217;s diet and ensure that the correct foods are being eaten.</p>
<p>It has been found through research that  sugar (and sugar-rich foods) promotes yeast growth. Therefore it follows that by decreasing  the intake of sugar will  help decrease yeast level in the body. It has also been discovered that eating yogurt will help decrease the amount of <a href="http://www.yeastinfectionreliefblog.com/yeastinfectionomore" target="_blank">yeast infection </a>in the body.</p>
