 photo credit: soylentgreen23 How do women get a yeast infection? Under normal circumstances, Candida albicans, a naturally occurring strain of yeast, can survive in the vagina without posing harm or leading to symptoms in the host. However, it can easily proliferate. If uncontrolled, chronic vaginal yeast infections will ensue, wreaking havoc on body systems [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><a title="Holding Gustav" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/94032388@N00/3708967853/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="border: 0px;" title="get a yeast infection" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2480/3708967853_f281dfcd3c_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Holding Gustav" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution-ShareAlike License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.yeastinfectionreliefblog.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="soylentgreen23" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/94032388@N00/3708967853/" target="_blank">soylentgreen23</a></small> How do women get a <a href="http://www.yeastinfectionreliefblog.com/yeastinfectionomore" target="_blank">yeast infection</a>? Under normal circum<span style="color: #000000;">stances, Candida albicans, a naturally occurring strain of yeast, can survive in the vagina without posing harm or leading to symptoms in the host. However, it can easily proliferate</span>. If uncontrolled, chronic vaginal yeast infections will ensue, wreaking havoc on body systems and overall wellness.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;">Among the most common causes of the breakdown of friendly flora are use of antibiotics, steroids, or oral contraceptives/birth control pills. Changes in the pH balance of the vagina or hormonal body changes brought on by pregnancy or regular intake of birth control pills also predispose women to <a href="http://www.yeastinfectionreliefblog.com/yeastinfectionomore" target="_blank">yeast infection</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
